Dialogs.Dialog: Well, ...., Rinko will cook, so would you like to come to my house for dinner？ It's ok if you can't.
Really？ Hehe.... then, I'll go home first after school and wait for you, so you can come when you're ready.
Heh, ...., I knew you'd say that. I'll be ready then, I'll see you later.
Yea, I'll leave it to you.
I'm not sure I can make it today. .... Sorry.
Oh, It's ok. I don't mind....
This is the first time you've eaten at Rinko's house, isn't it？
Yes, that's right. I'm a little nervous.
It's not my first time, come on, come on. Just make yourself comfortable, okay？
Today, I wanted you to try a dish I recently learned to cook. Well, I guess you'll have to wait until it's ready.
I've got a menu in mind, but if there's anything you want to eat.... just let me know, okay？
I want to make a request
Okay. Well, I'll try to cook something I've learned recently.
Okay. Since we're going to the trouble, I'll make you something you'll like.
I think I'll request the ▲メニュー▲ then.
Here you go. I feel like I did a good job, so you can count on me.
Thank you for waiting. Well, please try it.
Sorry for the wait. I might have messed up a bit... But don't worry, you can eat it.
I'm trying something new. What do you think？
I'm putting my own twist on it this time.
I tried to arrange it in the Rinko style today, hehe.
Following a recipe is fine, but I think you're only a full-fledged professional when you can create using your own personality. What do you think？
I'm trying to be a little creative with today's dish. I wonder if you can tell the difference.
I was a little particular about the seasoning in this one. I wonder if you will like it...
I'm confident in my Japanese food. Well, you'll understand when you eat it.
I'm probably the best at Japanese food these days. I don't know if it's to your liking, though.
I've been enjoying the taste of Japanese food lately.
Western food has a wide range, but I think Rinko is rather good at it.
I'm confident in making western food these days.
I'll leave the seasoning of Western food up to you. It will definitely suit your palate.
I'm pretty proud of being able to make good Chinese food.
Rinko maybe is good at Chinese. Why don't you try it？ But I shouldn't just praise myself, hehe.
Lately, when I cook Chinese food, the taste and the oil level are just right. Maybe I just have a good sense？
I've been getting better at this kind of cooking lately. I think it's got good flavor, don't you？
How about a girlfriend who is good at this kind of cooking？ Hehe.
I've been getting good at this kind of cooking lately. I'm sure you'll say it's delicious.
Because with Rinko, any dish is perfect.
Lately, no matter what I make, it tastes good. I'm sure today's will be delicious too.
I wonder if Rinko has a sense for cooking？ I feel like saying that I'm good at all kinds of cooking.... hehe.
Somehow.... Japanese food is not good. I try my best to make it, but.... what am I missing？
Ha.... Japanese food is a delicate dish. I did my best in my own way, so.... try it.
I haven't been able to finish my Japanese food well lately. .... I've been working pretty hard on it, though.
You know, ...., I haven't been able to make Western food well lately. But I worked really hard on this one.
Western food looks simple, but it's really deep. I did my best today, so I think today's dish probably tastes good.
I've been having trouble with Western food lately. And today's dish, well... I worked really hard on it, ok？
It's hard to remember the steps in Chinese cooking, but there's always love in every step.
Chinese seasoning can be unique, right？ So even if this seasoning was unique, wouldn't .... that mean that it wasn't Rinko's fault？
Chinese is .... Hmm, it was still difficult.
I couldn't make this dish very well. .... But I worked pretty hard on it！
It's not that I skimped on this .... Rather, I put more effort into it than usual. ....
I tried my best to make it, but .... I'm not too sure about this dish.
Lately, I've been having trouble deciding on the taste.... no matter what I make. How can I make it more to your liking？
I'm not sure about cooking. .... I wish they would invent some kind of seasoning that anyone could use to make it taste good.
Why is cooking so difficult？ .... But I worked really hard on it, so you'll eat it, right？
Do you recognize these dishes？ It's the matching one that you gave me. Hehe.
I like these dishes. It's not because we're matching ....
Ah, I'm full. Thanks for the food！
(What is it.... I have a strange feeling that something good is about to happen)
So, how did it go？ I'm rather confident in myself.
(You sure did it well, didn't you？)
Well, tell me what you think？ I'm confident about today's, hehe.
(I think it was well done, don't you？)
Hey, you'll tell me what you think, right？ Because I'm confident today.
How was it？ Was it good？
Hey, can I ask you what you think？
(Well, well, what's there to complain about？)
....How was it？ I knew it wouldn't taste good.
(As expected, you look like it was a failure, ....)
....Do you want to tell me what you think？ If you don't like it, it's fine.
It's hard to say what you think...., right？
Really？ Yay！ Rinko worked really hard. Heh...
Really？ I'm glad. I felt pretty confident about it, too.
Eh, you thought so？ I thought.... it was an absolute failure. Maybe I'm out of sync.
I see. Then I guess I passed the test.
It was good in its own way.
Well, it was delicious as usual.
Really？ I'm okay with that one. .... Heh.
I guess it was a little too much for my taste.
Well, ...., I see. I thought I did well, but.... I'll have to reconsider.
I think I like a different flavoring better. ....
Oh, really？ Well, I'll study something different next time.
I wonder if it's not to ●'s liking？
....I see. I kind of knew that. I'll try to make it better next time.
Hey ...., would you like to have some days when you don't eat a bento？
Maybe we can go to the school cafeteria ....
If it's hard for ▲小早川＊▲ then it's ok, but I like your bentos.
Really？ Well then, I'll go make some more.
▲小早川＊▲ is going to have a hard time, and I'm sure the school cafeteria will be fine.
I see. Well, I don't mind, but it might be fun to go to the cafeteria.
Hey, what do you usually do for breakfast？
Well, why don't you let me make one for you next time？ But if you don't like it, don't force it.
How was breakfast the other day？ If you want, I can go and make it again.
I think I'll prepare it myself
It would be great if you could prepare breakfast for me.
I want to make my own breakfast ....
Wow, ...., I see. That's fine then.
Lately, I've been into making sweets. Would you like to try some？
Of course I want to try it.
Hehe .... Ok. I'll make it for you next time.
Hey, .... can I go make dinner again？
If you don't mind, please take care of ▲小早川＊▲.
Okay. I'll go make it next time, so please look forward to it until then.
I want to make as much as possible by myself....
